Pinch us—we just won Founder of the Year by Global Spa!

We’re beyond grateful for this recognition, but let’s be real—Suroskie isn’t just about the founders.

It’s about the whole team that pours their heart into every product and YOU—our community—who believed in us, supported us, and made this dream a reality.

This one’s for all of us. Thank you for making Suroskie what it is today.
